company <- read_xls("industry.xls")
company <- company[,c(1,5)]
company <- company[-c(1,nrow(company)),]
names(company) <- c("Time", "TotalUsage")

#season
company$season <- rep(rep(1:4, each = 3), times = 36)
company$season <- as.factor(company$season)

3. Data Structure

#str(industry)
company$Time <- sapply(company$Time, function(x){
  paste0(x,"-01")
})
company$Time <- as.POSIXct(company$Time, format = "%Y-%m-%d")
company$TotalUsage <- as.numeric(company$TotalUsage)

Variables

1. Arrange Function

argv.fun <- function(v) {
  v[,1] <- sapply(v[,1], function(x) {
  x %<>% sub("M", "-", .) %<>% paste0(., "-01")})
  v[,1] <- as.POSIXct(v[,1], format = "%Y-%m-%d")
  row.names(v) <- v[,1]
  v <- v[-(1:grep("2000", v[,1])[12]), ]
  v <- v[,-1]
  return(v)
}
#arrange function for employed population data
argp.fun <- function(v) {
  v[,1] <- sapply(v[,1], function(x) {
  x %<>% sub("M", "-", .) %<>% paste0(., "-01")})
  v[,1] <- as.POSIXct(v[,1], format = "%Y-%m-%d")
  row.names(v) <- v[,1]
  v <- v[,-1]
  return(v)
}

2. Read Variable

#就業人口 (19 variables)
pop1 <- read.csv("2001-11就業人口.csv", header = T, skip = 4,
                 nrows = 132, fileEncoding = "Big5")

pop2 <- read.csv("2012-16就業人口.csv",header = T, skip = 4,
                 nrows = 60, fileEncoding = "Big5")
pop3 <- read.csv("2017就業人口.csv", header = T, skip = 4,
                 nrows = 12, fileEncoding = "Big5")
#unify colnames
names(pop1) <- names(pop3)
names(pop2) <- names(pop3)
population <- rbind(pop1, pop2, pop3)
population <- argp.fun(population)
rm(pop1, pop2, pop3)
population <- rbind(population, rep("就業人口", length(population)))


#薪資 (41 variables)
wage <- read.csv("薪資.csv", header = T, skip = 4,
                 nrows = 432, fileEncoding = "Big5")
#missing
wage <- wage[,-40]
wage <- argv.fun(wage)
wage <- rbind(wage, rep("薪資", length(wage)))

#物價 (7 variables)
price <- read.csv("物價.csv", header = T, skip = 3,
                  nrows = 432, fileEncoding = "Big5")
price <- argv.fun(price)
price <- rbind(price, rep("物價", length(price)))

#五大銀行放款利率 (4 variables)
rate <- read.csv("放款利率.csv", header = T, skip = 3,
                 nrows = 252, fileEncoding = "Big5")
rate <- argv.fun(rate)
rate <- rbind(rate, rep("放款利率", length(rate)))

#原油價格 (2 variables)
oil <- read_xlsx("oil_price.xlsx", skip = 10, n_max = 456)
oil <- as.data.frame(oil) 
oil <- argv.fun(oil)
oil <- rbind(oil, rep("原油價格", length(oil)))

#combine all variables
v <- cbind(population, price, wage, rate, oil)

Plot Quarter

company$quarter <- rep(1:144, each = 3)
#quarter的usage
quarter.usage <- sapply(1:144, function(x){
  sum(company[company$quarter == x, "TotalUsage"])
})
#quater time
quarter.time <- paste0(rep(1982:2017, each = 4), '-', rep(c(1,4,7,10), times = 36))
#合併
quarter.file <- data.frame(Quarter = quarter.time, Usage = quarter.usage,
                           stringsAsFactors = F)
#補一個index

quarter.file %>%
  ggplot(data = .) +
  geom_line(aes(x = Quarter, y = Usage, color = index, group = 1), size = 1.2) +
  scale_x_discrete(breaks = paste0(1982:2017, -1), labels = 1982:2017) +

  theme_bw() +

GDP

argg.fun <- function(v) {
  v[,1] <- as.POSIXct(v[,1], format = "%Y-%m-%d")
  row.names(v) <- v[,1]
  v <- v[,-1]
  return(v)
}
gdp <- read.csv("各產業GDP.csv", header = F, skip = 4, nrows = 1360) 
GDP <- data.frame(matrix(gdp$V3[-seq(1,1360,20)], ncol = 19, byrow = T))
colnames(GDP) <- gdp$V2[2:20]
GDP <- cbind(c(paste0(rep(2001:2017, each = 4), '-', 
                       rep(c('01','04','07','10'), times = 17), '-01')), GDP)
GDP <- argg.fun(GDP)
rm(gdp)

Transform to TS

#選取2001~2017年的月資料
new.company <- company %>%
  subset(Time < as.POSIXct("2016-01-01", format = "%Y-%m-%d")) 
test.company <- company %>%
  subset(Time > as.POSIXct("2015-12-01", format = "%Y-%m-%d")) 

new.company %$%
  ts(TotalUsage, start = c(1982, 1), frequency = 12) -> ts.file
test.company %$%

2. ACF/PACF-1

tsdisplay(log(ts.file))

\ 從自相關係數可以看出，當期的用電量與前幾期是有相關的，且折線圖看出它有上升的趨勢，為了使其平穩，我會採取差分的方法。

3. ADF-1

#library(tseries)
#ADF檢定
#tseries::adf.test(log(ts.file), k = 12, alternative = "stationary")
#畫圖

library("CADFtest")
## Warning: package 'CADFtest' was built under R version 3.4.4
## Loading required package: dynlm
## Warning: package 'dynlm' was built under R version 3.4.4
## Loading required package: urca
## Warning: package 'urca' was built under R version 3.4.4
CADFtest(log(ts.file), max.lag.y = 12, type = "trend", criterion = "AIC")
## 
##  ADF test
## 
## data:  log(ts.file)
## ADF(11) = -0.55757, p-value = 0.9805
## alternative hypothesis: true delta is less than 0
## sample estimates:
##       delta 
## -0.02039638

\ 使用CADFtest 單根檢定，考慮趨勢項和常數項，並以AIC選擇最適當的模型，檢定結果：落後期為11期，p-value = 0.9805 > 0.05，在95％的信心水準下，不拒絕虛無假設，此序列具有單根。

6. ADF-2

library("CADFtest")
CADFtest(diff(log(ts.file)), max.lag.y = 10, type = "trend", criterion = "AIC")
## 
##  ADF test
## 
## data:  diff(log(ts.file))
## ADF(10) = -22.669, p-value < 2.2e-16
## alternative hypothesis: true delta is less than 0
## sample estimates:
##     delta 
## -9.090716

使用CADFtest 單根檢定，以AIC選擇最適當的模型，檢定結果：落後期為1期，p-value < 0.05，在95％的信心水準下，拒絕虛無假設，此序列已不具有單根。
